{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"2154","airdate":"1552417200","name_switch":"off","DJ":"ziona and Slaygon","showname":"Greek talk with Vaggelis","blurb":"Hello All of you! \n\nIt wasn't such a long time ago when we announced the winners of the ROTY Awards 2018. And the time has come to introduce our Newcomer of the year! \n\nVaggelis Papadopoulos comes from the sunny land of Greece and amazed everyone with his rockmetal covers last year. We will have a lot of questions for him, and of course you can have yours too!\n\nAnd don't worry - We won't be talking Greek!\n\nWe welcome him on air at 9 PM after the warmup hour, when you can have your requests as usual. \nMake sure you SLAY tuned with us and this cheerful guy! ","nice_showname":"<strong><big>ziona and Slaygon<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Greek talk with Vaggelis","nice_airdate":"Tuesday 12th March, 2019<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"}]}